int val = 83;
int* result = find(begin(ia), end(ia), val);


count
vector v1{4,5,30,1,3,9,10,3};
auto ret = count(v1.cbegin(),v1.cend(),3);


accumulate
accumulate的第三个参数类型决定了函数中使用哪个加法运算符以及返回值的类型。
```cpp
